de.embl.rieslab.emu.swinglisteners

Class SwingComponentTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.embl.rieslab.emu.swinglisteners.SwingComponentTests

  • public class SwingComponentTests
extends java.lang.Object
    These are just a bunch of tests to remember whether changing the state of a Swing JComponent fires the action listeners used in SwingUIListeners. This is important to know in the UIPlugin in order to avoid repeated calls to the MMProperty from ConfigurablePanel.propertyHashChanged(String, String).
    Author:
    Joran Deschamps
